version_description:
* Added Drawing - Fill the topics with hand-drawn document, or drawing from Apple Pencil.
* Added Outliner Mode - A new way to read and edit your mind map in the listing view, effective and fast;
* Supported Multiple Windows - Open, read and edit 2 files side by side in the same screen;
* Fixed the sliding input issue at English input;
* Fixed entering editing issue when double clicking the Topic;
* Fixed the ticking status issue of selecting Theme;
------------------------
Coming soon, with all new UI and user experience.

1. Fixed an issue of Boundary title editing failure；
2. Fixed an issue of content editing failure in the Matrix structure;
3. Fixed an issue of opening protected XMind file failure; 
4. Support clicking topic link and jumping to target topic;
5. Fixed an issue of new file auto-renaming failure;
6. Fixed an issue of tapered line setting failure;;
7. Fixed some other known issues;

* Fixed the issue of image missing when pasting;
* Fixed the wrap issue when editing the topic;
* Modified the notice of opening an encrypted file;
* Fixed the issue of undo when editing;
* Tap to unfold the folded topic in searching results automatically;
* Tap the blank part of the sheet to close Format/Insert/More panel;
* Fixed some known bugs;

* Added Drawing - Fill the topics with hand-drawn document, or drawing from Apple Pencil.
* Added Outliner Mode - A new way to read and edit your mind map in the listing view, effective and fast;
* Supported Multiple Windows - Open, read and edit 2 files side by side in the same screen;
* Fixed the sliding input issue at English input;
* Fixed entering editing issue when double clicking the Topic;
* Fixed the ticking status issue of selecting Theme;
------------------------
Coming soon, with all new UI and user experience.

* Added & updated multiple themes;
* Fixed the issue of color setting in some cases;
* Fixed the crash issue of when opening Airdrop files;
* Fixed the open issue of XMind files in third-party apps in iOS 12;
* Fixed the irresponsive issue when opening encrypted files;
* Fixed the oversized blank space issue when exporting pictures;
* Fixed the selected state display of the Topic in exported PDF;
--------
Notice: Drawing requires iOS 13 or above.

* Add NeverMind, an original typeface designed by XMind;
* Support brand new Marker;
* Fixed the display issue when inputting in the Topic under some circumstances;
* Fixed the crash issue when connecting iPad to external monitor;
* Fixed the issue of disordered sheet positions when switching back to XMind from other programs;
* Fixed the issue of generating incorrect thumbnails of some files;

1. Fixed the crash issue in special circumstances;
2. Fixed an content loss issue when clicking other bottons while editing a topic;
3. Fixed other known issues;

1. Added Indonesian, Italian, Korean, Portuguese, Russian, Spanish, Thai language support;
2. Optimized the display effect of equation;
3. Image display supported by Outliner;
4. Fixed the issue that cannot export as png to Telegram;
5. Fixed some other known issues;

1. Improved mouse support function on iOS 13.4;
2. Fixed a bug where texts aren’t automatically selected all when editing a new topic in some languages including Indonesian, Italian, Korean, Portuguese, Russian, Spanish, Thai;
3. Fixed a bug that may cause the app to crash due to Airdrop files;
4. Fixed some other known issues.

1. Added the Drawing feature on Photo;
2. Optimized the content display of Outliner;
3. Fixed the crash issue when running Outliner in special cases;
4. Fixed the issue that the text in topic may be replaced in special cases;
5. Fixed other known issues;

1. Added Brace Map - a structure that describes the relationship between the whole and the part;
2. Added Label and Marker display in the Outliner;
3. Fixed other known issues.

1. Fixed the issue of Relationship display error in PNG and PDF;
2. Added Outliner printing feature;
3. Added the feature of exporting Outliner to PDF.

1. Fixed the problem that a mind map cannot be set with a transparent background;
2. Fixed the problem that some content was not saved in time when sharing to other apps;
3. Fixed other known problems.

1. In this version, we have fixed mouse operation failure issue when switching applications;
2. The operation logic of the  up and down arrow on keyboard in the Outliner has been optimized;
3. When sharing XMind files, it will be moved to the target location instead of being copied under special  circumstances. This issue has been fixed already.

• Modify the font size and manual width by entering values manually;
• Long press the undo button to redo previous operations in split and compact view;
• You are able to save multiple versions of the same file if conflicts occur in iCloud Drive;
• Double-tap the blank area to display a complete sheet that fits screen;
• Fixed inaccurate redirection of some topic links;
• Fixed the insert problem of elements in the summary;
• Fixed the issue of inconsistent font styles in exported PNG/PDF;
• Fixed known bugs with improvements.
----------------
Reminder:
If you cannot access to all the features with subscription, please follow the steps below to solve the issue:
1. Tap “Settings” in the upper-right corner of the Document Browser Page, and tap “Restore Purchase”. 
2. Re-verify and bind the payment credentials of the account.
